1000-mirrors-challenge/
├── run_mirror.py              # main script (one-click)
├── sacred_mirror_prompt.txt   # exact prompt (never changes)
├── proofs/                    # generated folder
├── keys/                      # your ed25519 keypair (gitignored)
├── witness.jsonl              # master append-only log
├── submit_to_chain.py         # optional: posts hashes to Ethereum/Polygon/Solana
├── Dockerfile
├── README.md
└── requirements.txt
